{"tid":825611,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"暑假工問題","createTime":"2018-09-17T16:20:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T04:33:37.000Z","uid":84442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b0eadf13f56292cc411bc048bbf9dd9aa2476a00","tid":825611,"uid":84442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T16:20:29.000Z","msg":"暑假工<br />\n做兩個半月<br />\n計月薪<br />\n諗住人工算係咁<br />\n點知最尾半個月<br />\n份糧係咁樣計<br />\n因為我返左11日<br />\n11/31*月薪<br />\n總結返我返咁多日<br />\n原來時薪得50蚊<br />\n即係比人搵左笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實係咪正常<br />\n份約只係列明返工至8月尾<br />\n XX糧 同埋遲到會扣人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af1854a4b402ba7f1c39bebb1f1d695a954683d9","tid":825611,"uid":200165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T16:32:50.000Z","msg":"認真計過？"},{"pid":"9dd1304e5317110a319204b197166e522ad8a4a2","tid":825611,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T00:47:05.000Z","msg":"好多工都係你賠比佢就賠1/22或者該月日數<br />\n<br />\n佢賠比你就1/31"},{"pid":"91e226213f33fa9cf8626c38d70c5b303fb3c76d","tid":825611,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T01:32:18.000Z","msg":"暑期工都遲到就反省下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce0eef7a61db9e19db24a53cc20b7918ca233595","tid":825611,"uid":84442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af1854a4b402ba7f1c39bebb1f1d695a954683d9","tid":825611,"uid":200165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T16:32:50.000Z","msg":"認真計過？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:33:37.000Z","msg":"當初佢地話遲到請假就會扣到50時薪<br />\n結果最後先知原來一直都50時薪<br />\n簽左約又唔可以臨尾半個月遲職<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}